        | Víctor Valdés       | Jan 14, 1982 (42) | L’Hospitalet de Llobregat| 1.83 m | Spain       | Goalkeeper             | right | no agent                                   | /retired/startseite/verein/123              | Aug 17, 2017 | -           | null   | null      |
